thread.title: SunEdison to Buy 33% Interest in Dominion Portfolio of Solar Assets
thread.title_full: SunEdison to Buy 33% Interest in Dominion Portfolio of Solar Assets - WSJ

author: Tess Stynes
title: SunEdison to Buy 33% Interest in Dominion Portfolio of Solar Assets
text:
SunEdison Inc. agreed to acquire a 33% interest in a portfolio of solar assets from Dominion Resources Inc. for roughly $300 million, the latest in a recent string of deals between the companies.
Under the agreement, SunEdison also has an option to acquire the remaining stake in the portfolio, which includes 24 projects in California,...
